title: The Lone Ranger S01E13-E14
description:
The Lone Ranger

The Sole Survivor of a posse of Texas Rangers ambushed by a gang of desperados, John Reid was left for dead and nursed back to health by Tonto (Jay Silverheels), a friendly Indian whom he had once helped. With a black mask and silver bullets from the mine he discovered with his brother, one of the slain Rangers, Reid sets out astride his horse, Silver, to right the wrongs of the West as The Lone Ranger (Clayton Moore)

Episode 13 Finders Keepers

In "Finders Keepers," ex-con Nat Parker (Arthur Franz) is gunning for his former partners in crime, but the Ranger and Beata (Carol Thurston_, the Gypsy girl who loves Nat, will keep him on the straight and narrow. Then,

Episode 14 The Masked Rider

The Ranger poses as a criminal called "The Masked Rider" to help Sheriff Jim Hawks (Ed Rand), whose fiance, Nancy Barton (Nan Leslie), is being blackmailed into marrying Dirk Nelson (John Doucette). 

Approximately 46 Minutes
